Change Log

[0.1.0] - 2020-07-18

Added:
* Player's hp system.
* Implement trap.
* Player can go into toxic area where their hp will be continuously deducted.
* Player's conversation with NPC.
* Pause function.
* Sound effect when player step into a trap.
* Sound effect when player talks with NPCs.

Fixed:

* The bug which the trap will vanish while player is not on it.
* The bug that sound effect will repeat itself while player step into the trap.